examples.en: The workers descended into the hole.
The stairs descended into the tunnel.
The manor descended to his son.
A feeling of sadness descended on me.
He turned from the road, and descended the path towards the hut.
examples.ru: Он свернул с дороги и по тропинке стал спускаться к хижине.

examples.en: The situation descended into utter chaos.
A herd of goats descended into the valley.
The children descended the staircase silently.
I am descended maternally from the family of Rose.
examples.ru: По материнской линии я происхожу из семьи Розы.

examples.en: He fought down his terror as darkness descended, and walked on through the wood.
examples.ru: Когда стемнело, он поборол страх и пошёл дальше через лес.

examples.en: A cloud of gloom has descended over the city.
examples.ru: На город опустилось облако тоски и уныния.

examples.en: The country had descended into economic chaos.
She was descended from an old Italian noble family.
examples.ru: Она происходила из старой итальянской дворянской семьи.
